Professional Services

Company Overview of Glenbrook Partners LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Glenbrook Partners LLC offers clients strategy consulting, research, and industry education programs in the United States. It offers various consulting services, including merchant acquirer RFP assistance; payments assessments that comprise contracts and relationships, processing infrastructure, cards, payment optimization and customization, ACH, payments organization, reporting and KPIs, customer impact, sustainability, and product management; and strategy consulting services, which include opportunity identification and assessment, product strategy development, product definition, market and competitive analysis, market sizing, channel strategy, pricing strategy, risk management, partnersh...
Glenbrook Partners LLC offers clients strategy consulting, research, and industry education programs in the United States. It offers various consulting services, including merchant acquirer RFP assistance; payments assessments that comprise contracts and relationships, processing infrastructure, cards, payment optimization and customization, ACH, payments organization, reporting and KPIs, customer impact, sustainability, and product management; and strategy consulting services, which include opportunity identification and assessment, product strategy development, product definition, market and competitive analysis, market sizing, channel strategy, pricing strategy, risk management, partnership evaluation and strategic sourcing, and concept testing. The company also offers consulting services to industry groups; industry scan programs, such as market reports, competitive assessments, and customized consulting engagements; investor due diligence analysis, including market assessment and technology due diligence analysis; and financial institutions payments strategy programs. In addition, it offers education programs, including boot camps, private workshops, and insight workshops. The company serves payments service providers, card networks, technology and risk management companies, banks, merchants, and treasury managers. Glenbrook Partners LLC was founded in 2001 and is based in Menlo Park, California.
Detailed Description


