Beth Horowitz Steel Joins Glenbrook Partners as Partner
Apr 4 16
Glenbrook Partners announced that Beth Horowitz Steel has joined the firm as a partner. Beth is a transformational business leader who has developed new products, created successful partnerships, and driven technology and marketing innovation throughout her 25 year career in the payments industry. As an independent consultant since 2014, Beth led consulting engagements for banks, financial services organizations, and early stage Fintech companies, across a variety of strategic, product, and market development areas.


