What We DoFounded in 2001, Glenbrook is a payments industry strategy consulting and research firm.  We bring to our clients a unique combination of our specialized skills in payments, many years of hands-on experience in the field, and our network of professional relationships.Glenbrook serves payments professionals in many different kinds of companies across the payments industry.  We enjoy meeting and working with start-ups as well as managers from leading companies that are looking to innovate.  Learn more about Glenbrook & our clients. Deep KnowledgeWe provide deep knowledge on how payment systems work and are used.Discipline
Our disciplined approach to consulting assignments and research projects ensures rigorous analysis and intelligent results. CuriosityWe explore how the industry is changing, and how technical, regulatory & economic levers are being moved. Insights & OpinionsWe share our insights on what is happening in the industry and why. Latest News
PaymentsNews.com is the industry leading news blog.  Daily headline news summaries and articles are carefully selected by Glenbrook's editor. RSS feeds and email subscriptions are available.

